---
title: Indian Coconut Chicken Curry with Garlic Rice & Yoghurt
description: Rich, creamy and aromatic – this mild curry has all the elements that make Indian food so appealing. Packed with flavour, it comes together fast for a mouth-watering meal that the troops will love!
